&lt;p&gt;143 Studios is hiring a&lt;strong&gt; Customer Support + Social Engagement Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to help strengthen how we listen, respond, route and learn from our audience across inbox, social and podcast channels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
