&lt;p&gt;This role will also support the implementation and ongoing use of a new inbox support tool, workflow and tagging system. You will help create the structure around how inbound messages are categorized, routed, tracked, reported and turned into useful insights for the Community team, leadership, and cross-functional teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
