&lt;li&gt;Monitor and manage the customer support inboxes daily&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to customer, subscriber, listener, and fan inquiries with clarity, care and accuracy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot basic issues and provide relevant resources, including podcast episodes, articles, product links, or approved support materials&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Categorize, prioritize and manage a high volume of messages efficiently without sacrificing quality or empathy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain organized and accurate records in the ticketing system&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use tracking systems to ensure timely follow-up and resolution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forward or escalate inquiries to the appropriate internal teams, agencies or team leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond using approved messaging while maintaining the Mel Robbins brand voice&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in updating templates, macros, FAQs and support processes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all communication reflects the brand tone: motivational, compassionate, clear and direct&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
